# Install "REST Client" (humao.rest-client), then use "Send Request" above each block.
#
# Cursor: the HTML response side panel often stays blank (github.com/Huachao/vscode-restclient/issues/1434).
# This workspace sets rest-client.previewResponseInUntitledDocument so the response opens in an editor tab
# where you can read it and use Save Full Response / Save Response Body in the tab toolbar.
# Workaround if you still use the HTML panel: split the editor (Cmd+\ on macOS) before sending.

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000
@contentType = application/json

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: {{contentType}}

### List agents
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/agents
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Run agent — summary
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/agents/run
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "agent_type": "summary_agent",
  "input_text": "LangGraph helps you build stateful, multi-step LLM workflows."
}

### Run agent — tool_agent (LLM may call tools; response has no tool trace)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/agents/run
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "agent_type": "tool_agent",
  "input_text": "Add 12.5 and 7.3, then slugify: LangGraph Tool Calling Demo"
}

### Run agent with trace — tool_agent (returns tool_calls in response)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/agents/run-with-trace
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "agent_type": "tool_agent",
  "input_text": "What time is it in UTC? Count words in: LangGraph tool call demo"
}

### Collaborative workflow
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/agents/workflow
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "input_text": "Create a short launch plan for an AI chatbot and output in English."
}

### LangGraph — checkpoint (same thread_id = same conversation)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/agents/demo/checkpoint
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "thread_id": "http-demo-1",
  "input_text": "My codename is Bluejay. Acknowledge in one sentence."
}

### LangGraph — checkpoint (follow-up; reuse thread_id)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/agents/demo/checkpoint
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "thread_id": "http-demo-1",
  "input_text": "What was my codename?"
}

### LangGraph — conditional route (math vs general)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/agents/demo/conditional-route
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "input_text": "Calculate 12.5 + 7.3 in one line."
}

### LangGraph — prebuilt ReAct agent
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/agents/demo/react-agent
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "input_text": "What time is it in UTC? Then add 3 and 5."
}

### List tools (direct backend calls, no LLM)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tools
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Execute tool — add_numbers
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tools
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "tool_name": "add_numbers",
  "arguments": { "a": 12.5, "b": 7.3 }
}

### Execute tool — count_words
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tools
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "tool_name": "count_words",
  "arguments": { "text": "one two three four" }
}
